{"tid":776303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 巴基斯坦】不容許中國人在當地開採黃金 中國工程師被炸彈攻擊","createTime":"2018-08-12T02:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T00:24:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1513527c261f43586d78faacbb3d603c91a0ece6","tid":776303,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"一輛載有中國工程師團隊的巴士，周六（11日）在巴基斯坦西部城鎮達爾本丁（Dalbandin）遭到自殺炸彈攻擊，炸彈客粉身碎骨，而巴士上有6人受傷，包括3名中國人。當地分離組織「俾路支解放軍」（Balochistan Liberation Army）聲稱犯案，強調不會容許中國人在當地開採黃金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ny/realtime/20180812/1409312/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fny%2Frealtime%2F20180812%2F1409312%2F&d=wJZSepfUpgmTDB9HfkVJRzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9c6eb884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fny%2Frealtime%2F20180812%2F1409312%2F&h=e4387eb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ny/realtime/20180812/1409312/</a>"},{"pid":"9644edb56459dde48f07714b42567b8d30514bff","tid":776303,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"勇武"},{"pid":"62773bbfc84d30521b93308ab663bb1015a94346","tid":776303,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"真勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717ab2a5f4d5efe01c642c46eb78ee018db3d06b","tid":776303,"uid":19454,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/102818_dc7a68256dd0f3cb288952606009ce01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F102818_dc7a68256dd0f3cb288952606009ce01.png&h=d5b620f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"207496382a7f9c10cb301b4c77bd71f21d4285ae","tid":776303,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"